      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORLESS THE KING (1) jumped cleanly from the rails last start to lead all the way and score (18.61) at this track in a Maiden over 320m. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can make it two on the bounce. VONNIE LEE (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (23.86) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to feature. SHOT OF FAITH (8) tackled far tougher grade latest but ran very well to hit the frame when 3rd (18.57) at this track in Mix 1/2/3. Scored at this track in weaker company the previous run. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Will give a great sight again. MIDNIGHT KELLY (6) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
